title: 'A super knock' - Carey scores century to help Australia past 300
subtitle: Alex Carey frustrates England as he scores 106, his third career Test century, and his first against England, to help Australia recover from 94-4 to 307-7 on day one of the third Ashes Test in Adelaide.
full_text: Alex Carey frustrates England as he scores 106, his third career Test century, and his first against England, to help Australia recover from 94-4 to 307-7 on day one of the third Ashes Test in Adelaide.
